data.description:
Dream no more! 35 Acres & a barndominium, what more could you ask for? Bring the horses. The land already has pastures, round pen, arena & riding trails. There are 4 very nice stalls & open area for tack storage and more. The house part has been set up for full time living or 2 Airbnb units. The kitchen wiring and plumbing is in place upstairs for a future Airbnb. There are two large porches for relaxation, cooking out and enjoying the views. The property has a gated entrance for extra privacy.  The original house portion downstairs, was built in 2008 and upstairs was finished in 2023. 
Easy commute to Rock Hill
